
COMMON LINUX/UNlX PROBLEMS & SOLUTIONS

1) AA's alarm speech is very delayed compared to the textual notification banner
  
   In Ubuntu 11.10 (and 12.04 as well, it seems) this is caused by a strage
   Ubuntu bug when having bluez-alsa installed. You should uninstall bluez-alsa.
   Here is the Ubuntu bug page:
   https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/bluez/+bug/1025578


